thread.title: Infoblox shares climb on better-than-expected results
thread.title_full: Infoblox shares climb on better-than-expected results - MarketWatch

author: Sue Chang
title: Infoblox shares climb on better-than-expected results
text: Shares of Infoblox Inc. BLOX, -0.75% rallied in Thursday's extended trade after the network controls company reported better-than-expected quarterly results. Infoblox posted a fiscal fourth-quarter loss of $4.7 million, or 8 cents a share, narrowing from a loss of $9.5 million, or 17 cents a share, a year ago. On an adjusted basis, the company earned 12 cents a share, ahead of the 10 cents a share forecast by analysts in a FactSet survey. Revenue grew 34% to $87 million, which also beat expectations of $80.5 million. Infoblox shares were up 5.7% in the after-hours session.
